            objectives: 'The goal of this work is to build the behaviour  for an agent (or robot) that can act in a story where other agents and humans participate. The story, as such, will emerge from the actions of the agents as actors. This roleplay environment will be targeting entertainment agents/robots and we will explore the possibility of collaborating with a museum to test the work done. \nThis is a multidisciplinary work that involves two main areas:\n\n- virtual storytelling and entertainment computing\n- social agents/robots\n\nThe expected work should produce a theatre scene that can be acted out by the agents with humans. \nInitially the work will also involve the collection of data (from people) that will allow for the creation of the decision making of the agents.\n',
