            objectives: 'The LdoD Archive supports the definition of virtual editions of the Fernando Pessoa&#39;s Book of Disquiet. In this work we intend to extend the existing system to incorporate the ability to include citations of the LdoD on social media, using automatic techniques, where the system is able to automatically collect citations from a predefined set of social media feeds.',
