            observations: 'There is an external co-advisor: Friedrich Steimann (Friedrich.Steimann@fernuni-hagen.de)',
            objectives: 'The objective of this thesis is an investigation of “unit” tests found in the wild (i.e., version control systems, such as github) and whether they actually are unit tests or more like integration tests. This is an important study has it impacts many other domains, such as testing, and automatic debugging.\n\nYet another objective is to build a toolset to visualize that information such that the programmer get a sense of whether to add more unit tests or integration tests. ',
