            vacancies: '0',
            location: ' IST/Instituto das Telecomunicações, Torre Norte - 9. Piso.',
            courses: 'MEIC-A, MEIC-T',
            observations: 'Prof. Nuno Horta, nuno.horta@lx.it.pt ou 218418093\n\nPossível atribuição de 1 (de 5) bolsas de investigação no total de 1K€ no semestre da tese dependendo do desempenho do candidato, só aplicável a candidatos com elevada disponibilidade no semestre da tese.',
            objectives: 'This proposal aims at first studying the state-of-the-art electronic design automation tools, such as AIDAsoft www.aidasoft.com, defining, implementing and testing a set of benchmarks to be proposed for the EDA industry. This type of benchmarks is not available yet and should be defined in a way to be machine and software independent, as well as, sufficiently wide-ranging to cover different class of evaluation metrics. The potential impact of work clearly foresees the publication of the work in international conferences and journals. The work will be based on the work already developed in terms of EDA solutions for analog IC design by the Integrated Circuit Group at Instituto de Telecomunicações and supervised by and internationally recognized team in the area.',
