            objectives: 'The LdoD Archive supports the definition of virtual editions of the Fernando Pessoa&#39;s Book of Disquiet. In this work we intend to extend the existing system to incorporate the ability to include two types of citations of the LdoD, scholar and social media citations, using a crowdsourcing technique, where any person can submit citations in the archive.\n\nAdditionally, we intend to implement a revision workflow, where crowd submitted citations are reviewed and classified previously to be made public in the archive',
